{"tid":917134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前民政事務局局長 何志平涉嫌賄賂烏干達及乍得政府官員案開審✌🏻","createTime":"2018-11-26T07:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T16:19:26.000Z","uid":13663,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e0482964360c0c5287eec09892ea27ae6c6c0ee3","tid":917134,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"民政事務局前局長何志平還柙超過1年後，其涉貪案將於美國時間11月26日（周一）開審。這宗涉及近300萬美元的貪污及洗黑錢案，牽扯兩位非洲國家元首、一位聯合國大會主席、一間中資石油企業、以及中共「一帶一路」國策。最高面臨85年監禁的何志平在開審前，已表明不會認罪，《蘋果》遠赴美國直擊審訊前，先與讀者重溫現時已掌握的案情。<br />\n<br />\n何志平在案中的身份，是由中國華信能源全資成立的「中華能源基金會（基金會）」秘書長。基金會是聯合國一個理事會的「特別諮詢非政府組織」，可出席聯合國的大小會議和論壇，何志平亦藉此自由進出聯合國，與各國領袖及代表接觸。本案涉及的烏干達案及乍得案，何志平均通過聯合國這個平台搭路，一步一步接觸到兩個國家的元首，從而為華信爭取商業利益。"},{"pid":"66f9f177fc42e6fac88dbd0f0c3f731461bc73b3","tid":917134,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181126/58950611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181126%2F58950611&d=ihKXy5AFm8UklAqt1nq4ZdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6b19aee8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181126%2F58950611&h=32f84e85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181126/58950611</a>"},{"pid":"cef6ac715fe75358932f71525c674f3607d843e3","tid":917134,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cf2a23127f5d5fd45a3d473a5c3cd5abd36a52","tid":917134,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">中華人民共和國香港特別行政區</span>民政事務局前局長何志平還柙超過1年後，其涉貪案將於美國時間11月26日（周一）開審。這宗涉及近300萬美元的貪污及洗黑錢案，牽扯兩位非洲國家元首、一位聯合國大會主席、一間中資石油企業、以及中共「一帶一路」國策。最高面臨85年監禁的何志平在開審前，已表明不會認罪，《蘋果》遠赴美國直擊審訊前，先與讀者重溫現時已掌握的案情。<br />\n<br />\n何志平在案中的身份，是由中國華信能源全資成立的「中華能源基金會（基金會）」秘書長。基金會是聯合國一個理事會的「特別諮詢非政府組織」，可出席聯合國的大小會議和論壇，何志平亦藉此自由進出聯合國，與各國領袖及代表接觸。本案涉及的烏干達案及查德案，何志平均通過聯合國這個平台搭路，一步一步接觸到兩個國家的元首，從而為華信爭取商業利益。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f1b4b76c03c25b24fecd3f2b1cfcf3c26ed233a2","tid":917134,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 期待期待"},{"pid":"05aae16631624ef929904f632bbb4ed3568901b9","tid":917134,"uid":44486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:07:21.000Z","msg":"坐左成年監<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbf36a4f132a43bd1e13ad26faece699c951ce2","tid":917134,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:07:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181126/58961823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181126%2F58961823&d=ihKXy5AFm8UklAqt1nq4ZdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=25085667\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181126%2F58961823&h=cda391f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181126/58961823</a>"},{"pid":"936a9b4a3460236fc8e323030eedc00397c2f61c","tid":917134,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbbf36a4f132a43bd1e13ad26faece699c951ce2","tid":917134,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:07:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181126/58961823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181126%2F58961823&d=ihKXy5AFm8UklAqt1nq4ZdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=25085667\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fh